      <img src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-BwdVbtCv8O0/Vzkw5k_BeUI/AAAAAAAABAY/FOphy1-SGYg07i0vRq932zac0JlHy60FACLcB/s1600/Delicious-Pizza-HD-Wallpaper.jpg" alt="card__image" class="card__image" width="600">
    </div>
    <div class="card__body">
      <span class="tag tag-brown">Food</span>
      <h4>Delicious Food</h4>
      <p>Using purely soft brown sugar will give a caramel-treacle flavour that can overpower the chocolate and 
        the butteriness. It will also cause the cookie to spread less and have a softer texture.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card__footer">
      <div class="user">
        <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/40?img=2" alt="user__image" class="user__image">
        <div class="user__info">
          <h5>Jony Doe</h5>
          <small>Yesterday</small>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card__header">
      <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1366052585/photo/shot-of-a-group-of-friends-hanging-out-before-working-out-together.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=rj7LgjUuXde0eLWikS1rvDnsKDdBotgsy9eM5HDzko0=" alt="card__image" class="card__image" width="600">
    </div>
    <div class="card__body">
      <span class="tag tag-red">Healthy Life</span>
      <h4>What is the definition of Healthy Living?</h4>
      <p>Healthy Living is about taking responsibility for your decisions and making smart health choices 
        for today and for the future. So healthy living would consist of:</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card__footer">
      <div class="user">
        <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/40?img=3" alt="user__image" class="user__image">
        <div class="user__info">
          <h5>John Doe</h5>
          <small>2d ago</small>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
